admitPatient

public int admitPatient(Patient patient)
Admits a patient to the hospital, by finding an unoccupied bed and setting it's patient variable to the Patient parameter, it then changes the bed.occupied variable to true.

Parameters:
Patient - The Patient to be admitted to a free bed
Returns:
The index of the bed the patient has been placed in, if no bed found then return -1
